      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "It's hard to knock the form of MIND OVER MATTER (1) who has strung four wins together on the bounce and is racing high on confidence of late. Hoop Cormack has been in the saddle for all four victories and sticks again today. Rates the testing material against this line-up. TORANAGA (3) has won three of his past four at this circuit and will be rock-hard fit for this contest. Looms as the main danger. FARAWAY DOWNS (5) looked handy saluting at Mackay on debut before being tipped out for further time to furnish. Has since tuned up for this with a solid trial win and a strong showing while fresh is expected. BETTERLUCKNEXTTIME (2) again gets the services of Wiggins in the irons and will be at peak fitness for this. In the mix. EXCEEDINGLY BRAZEN (6) is a last-start winner who shouldn't be slept on.",
